							"string" : "Ward Cunningham‚Äôs *Folk Memory* describes a distributed-object ecosystem where:\n\n1. Objects live in many places.\n2. Objects carry state (local knowledge).\n3. Change radiates outward from loci of ‚Äúauthority.‚Äù\n4. Trails describe how updates propagate through a distributed neighborhood.\n5. Systems achieve coherence not through central coordination but through *local diffusion* of correction.\n"
