				"string" : "Objects in Folk Memory are not immutable. They are:\n\n* carriers of partial knowledge,\n* attracted to ‚Äúbetter‚Äù knowledge sources,\n* updated locally through a neighborhood relation.\n\nThis is structurally identical to Kohonen‚Äôs *model vectors* (reference vectors).\nKohonen describes these as ‚Äúprototypes that migrate to optimally represent the input distribution‚Äù (SOM 2001, Chap. 3) ."
