				"string" : "Ward says objects propagate ‚Äútrail updates‚Äù outward from authoritative sources.\nSOM: the BMU becomes the temporary ‚Äúlocal authority,‚Äù the best known representative of the current input.\n\nPromotion in Folk Memory =\n‚ÄúYour shard best matches the new event; now tell your neighbors how to adjust.‚Äù"
